com.yworks.yfiles.graphml

Annotation Type GraphML


  • @Target(value={TYPE,METHOD,FIELD})
 @Inherited
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface GraphML
    Custom attribute to control specific aspects of GraphML deserialization. The specialized XamlSerializer will evaluate this attribute to override its built in serialization rules. The main use cases for this attribute are to override object reference sharing, configure consistent member naming and handle legacy serialization.
    See Also:
    XamlSerializer
